<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_css"><sp_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css>/**main, body{
	background-color: $sf-navbar-offset-color;
}
.sf-navbar-offset{
	background-color: $sf-navbar-offset-color;
}

*/

.sf-light-grey-bg{
	background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}

.sf-double-padding{
	padding: 100px 0px;
}

.sf-text-content h1, 
.sf-text-content h2,
.sf-text-content h3,
.sf-text-content h4,
.sf-text-content h5,
.sf-text-content h6,
.sf-text-content p{
	padding: 8px;
  	color: $navbar-inverse-link-hover-color;
}

.sf-text-content ul li{
	min-height: 50px;
}

.sf-text-content ul li a{
	text-decoration: none;
  	color: $navbar-inverse-link-color;
  	font-size: 16px;
  	padding: 8px;
}

.sf-img-wrapper img{
	width: 100%;
}
.sf-img-wrapper p{
	color: $navbar-inverse-link-hover-color;
    font-style: bold;
}

//transition page for sidebar

section.page.sf-page{
  	position: relative;
  	top: 0px;
  	left: 0px;
	transition: width 300ms ease, left 300ms ease;
}
section.page.sf-page.shrink{
	width: calc(100% - 250px);
    left: 250px;
}

//index

.sf-hero{
	min-height: 600px;
  border-bottom: 15px solid $sp-navbar-divider-color;
}

.sf-side-padding{
	padding-left: 16px;
  	padding-right: 16px;
}


//Bootstrap panel override
.sf-panel-override{
	background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}
.sf-panel-override .panel,
.sf-panel-override .panel-heading{
	background-color: #1D0F29;
  	color: $navbar-inverse-link-hover-color;
  	border: none;
  	box-shadow: 0px 0px 8px 2px #E40C79;
  
}

.sf-panel-override .panel-body .list-group .list-group-item,
.sf-panel-override .panel-body .bs-callout-success{
	background-color: #E40C79;
  	color: $navbar-inverse-link-hover-color;
}

.sf-panel-override .panel-body .list-group .list-group-item a,
.sf-panel-override .panel-body .bs-callout-success a{
	color: $navbar-inverse-link-hover-color;
}

.sf-panel-override span > i.kb-star-on{
	color: #5CB85C !important;
}


</css><name>Sly Fox Default Styles</name><sys_class_name>sp_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-08-09 18:50:09</sys_created_on><sys_id>511895f607f530100dc4fa7f7c1ed0e7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>65</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Sly Fox Default Styles</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_css_511895f607f530100dc4fa7f7c1ed0e7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-08-27 11:56:01</sys_updated_on></sp_css></record_update>
